details.sectionContent: This is a debate round in which the participants will have to defend their automobile against other. The automobile they get will depend upon the message they get one day before the event. Elimination will be held and round 1 scores will be considered. Debate will be conducted for five minutes.

There is 3 page given in which you have to recreate Automobile logo. In second page you have to make rough 2D sketch of car. In last page you should write down general specification whichever you know. Best 5 to 6 team will be selected. (1 hour will be given )
